name: Equity Share Capital
description: Represents paid-up equity capital issued by the company to shareholders.

name: Capital Reserves
description: Reserves created from capital profits, not available for dividend distribution.

name: Capital Redemption Reserve
description: Reserve created on redemption of preference shares as per Companies Act.

name: Securities Premium
description: Premium received over face value of shares, restricted usage by law.

name: Debenture Redemption Reserve
description: Reserve maintained for redemption of debentures.

name: Revaluation Reserve
description: Arises from upward revaluation of assets, not distributable.

name: Share Options Outstanding
description: ESOP-related reserve pending exercise or lapse.

name: Surplus / Retained Earnings
description: Accumulated profits after dividends and transfers.

name: Share Warrants Money
description: Amount received against share warrants pending allotment.

name: Long Term Bonds
description: Bonds repayable after 12 months from reporting date.

name: Long Term Debentures
description: Debenture liabilities classified as long term.

name: Long Term - Secured Loan Account
description: Loans secured against assets with long tenure.

name: Term Loans – Other Parties
description: Long-term loans from NBFCs or institutions.

name: Deferred Payment Liabilities
description: Credit arrangements with deferred settlement terms.

name: Long-term Deposits Taken
description: Deposits accepted repayable after one year.

name: Finance Lease Obligations (LT)
description: Lease liabilities payable beyond one year.

name: Unsecured Long-term Loans
description: Loans without collateral, long-term in nature.

name: Deferred Tax Liabilities
description: Timing differences causing future tax outflow.

name: Loans repayable on demand from Banks (Bank OD)
Loans repayable on demand From Other Parties
Current maturities of long-term borrowings
description: Portion of LT loans due within a year.

name: Current maturities of finance lease obligations
description: Lease liability due within one year.

name: Interest accrued but not due on borrowings
Interest accrued and due on borrowings
Income received in advance / Unearned Revenue
Unpaid matured deposits and interest thereon
Unpaid matured debentures and interest thereon
Short term Provision for Employee Benefits
CWIP – Buildings
description: Capital work in progress for buildings.

name: Investments in Property - Non Current
description: Property held for rental or appreciation.
